data.description:
1711 N. 16 Ct., Hollywood
Desire Excellence?  This home is perfect for a family that’s looking for a home, a good investment and rewarding 2 Bedroom 2 bath Turn-Key Home. Includes a convenient 1 car garage and the newer circular driveway.
“SOON TO BE LISTED ON THE MARKET” Over 1,300 Total Sq Feet are S-P-R-E-A-D Out in this 7,029 SQ FT property with room for a pool. Secluded with a private fenced in yard. Service Alley in back. Stay cool under the Central A/C.  Built in 1952.  Lots of Upgrades including Hurricane Windows, Doors and Garage. $2,765 was the tax bill in 2022 w/homestead exception. The property has been well maintained and is currently getting freshly painted and touched up for showings to happen in July.  Located in a most desirable east of Federal Hwy.,  Hollywood Neighborhood. Close to Shopping, schools, gyms, transportation, and parks.  The Beach is less than 1 mile away!  More amenities to see during your private showing. We are excited to find a new owner for this home,
Let’s Make a Deal, Asking $650k.
Put this on your must see List ~ before it’s entered on the MLS.
Call or Text Rich Aube of For Life Realty @ (954) 336-5110
